OL,4,CTop German cleric asks to quit over
OL,5,CChurch sex abuse failures
OL,6, Germany's top Roman Catholic cleric,
OL,7, Cardinal Reinhard Marx, has offered his
OL,8, resignation to the Pope over the
OL,9, Church's child sexual abuse scandals.
OL,11,F"It is important to me to share the
OL,12,Fresponsibility for the catastrophe of
OL,13,Fthe sexual abuse by Church officials
OL,14,Fover the past decades," he said in a
OL,15,Fletter to Pope Francis.
OL,17,FHe is the Archbishop of Munich. The
OL,18,FPope is still considering his offer.
OL,20,FPope Francis has sent two bishops to
OL,21,FCologne to investigate abuse cases.
